43:03.782 --> 43:05.350
- YES, THANK YOU, MICHAEL.

43:05.383 --> 43:07.686
- HEY, THIS IS MY KID TOO.
IF ANYTHING HAPPENS TO HIM--

43:07.719 --> 43:08.854
- NOTHING'S GOING TO HAPPEN.

43:08.887 --> 43:10.355
I'M FINE.
WE'RE FINE.

43:10.388 --> 43:11.757
- THERE ARE A LOT OF WOMEN
WHO HAVE TO DO THIS

43:11.790 --> 43:13.258
AT THE END
OF THEIR PREGNANCY.

43:13.291 --> 43:15.727
- YET ANOTHER REASON
WHY I'M GLAD I'M A GUY.

43:15.761 --> 43:17.829
- STILL,
THERE ARE MANY PLEASURES.

43:17.863 --> 43:20.966
- ALONG WITH THE PAIN.

43:20.999 --> 43:24.602
- THERE.
ALL RIGHT, GET IN.

43:30.876 --> 43:33.845
- AND STAY IN.

43:33.879 --> 43:36.281
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING ELSE...

43:36.314 --> 43:38.383
CALL ME.

43:38.416 --> 43:41.987
OR BETTER YET,
I'LL CALL YOU...

43:42.020 --> 43:44.690
IN ABOUT AN HOUR.

43:53.899 --> 43:56.735
- OY, HE'S NEVER GOING
TO LEAVE ME ALONE, IS HE?

43:56.768 --> 43:59.270
- [chuckles]
PROBABLY NOT.

43:59.304 --> 44:01.272
- THEN THERE'S DEBBIE.
- WHERE'RE YOU GOING?

44:01.306 --> 44:02.841
- TO GET A BOTTLE OF WATER.
- I'LL GET IT.

44:02.874 --> 44:04.009
THE DOCTOR SAID
YOU'RE NOT TO MOVE.

44:04.042 --> 44:05.811
CHRIST, DON'T YOU LISTEN
TO ANYBODY?

44:05.844 --> 44:07.445
- IT'S JUST IN THE KITCHEN.

44:07.478 --> 44:09.280
- YOU CAN GO TO THE BATHROOM,
AND THAT'S IT.

44:09.314 --> 44:13.318
UNTIL THE BABY'S BORN,
I'M YOUR ARMS AND LEGS.

44:22.260 --> 44:25.163
- SO, I GUESS WE'RE STUCK.

44:25.196 --> 44:29.100
- YOU IN BED,
US WITH EACH OTHER.

44:29.134 --> 44:32.170
- FUNNY, ISN'T IT?

44:32.203 --> 44:35.140
- ACHINGLY.

44:36.842 --> 44:41.112
I'LL GET YOU YOUR WATER.

44:49.888 --> 44:51.790
- [over TV] A FINE MIST
THAT WON'T WEIGH HAIR DOWN

44:51.823 --> 44:53.959
SO EVEN FINE
OR THINNING HAIR LOOKS--

44:53.992 --> 44:57.195
- EVERY 3,000 MILES,
IF YOU WANT YOUR CAR TO RUN--

44:57.228 --> 44:59.097
- HEY, SPORT.

44:59.130 --> 45:01.366
I WAS WONDERING
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU.

45:01.399 --> 45:04.402
PEEL OFF THOSE PANTS
AND LET'S START THE CLOCK.

45:04.435 --> 45:08.106
- SORRY I'M LATE.
I WAS WITH SIERRA.

45:08.139 --> 45:09.808
I'M AFRAID YOU'RE
GOING TO HAVE TO DEAL

45:09.841 --> 45:11.977
WITH A VERY DISTRAUGHT FIANCEE
WHEN YOU GET HOME.

45:12.010 --> 45:16.147
- YOU DIDN'T TELL HER?
- NO, NO, OF COURSE NOT.

45:16.181 --> 45:18.416
I LEAVE THAT UP TO YOU.

45:18.449 --> 45:20.952
I JUST TOLD HER
I COULDN'T PLAN YOUR WEDDING.

45:20.986 --> 45:23.889
- OH. THAT.

45:27.025 --> 45:29.094
- SO, UM...

45:29.127 --> 45:30.829
WHEN ARE YOU
GOING TO TELL HER?

45:30.862 --> 45:33.131
- ABOUT WHAT?

45:33.164 --> 45:34.900
- ABOUT YOU.

45:34.933 --> 45:38.536
ABOUT ME.

45:38.569 --> 45:40.538
SHE LOVES YOU, YOU KNOW?

45:40.571 --> 45:44.409
MORE THAN LOVES YOU--
WORSHIPS YOU, ADORES YOU,

45:44.442 --> 45:47.012
BELIEVES IN YOU.

45:47.045 --> 45:49.414
YOU KNOW HOW HURT,
HOW DEVASTATED SHE'D BE

45:49.447 --> 45:52.250
IF SHE EVER FOUND OUT?

45:52.283 --> 45:55.286
- WHY WOULD SHE EVER FIND OUT?

45:55.320 --> 45:58.189
WHY SHOULD ANYBODY?

45:58.223 --> 46:02.260
- 'CAUSE IT'S THE TRUTH?
- OH, THE TRUTH IS...

46:02.293 --> 46:06.865
I HAVE NOTHING TO GAIN
AND EVERYTHING TO LOSE.

46:06.898 --> 46:10.401
YOU SEE, I'M AN INDUSTRY--

46:10.435 --> 46:14.005
DREW BOYD, INC.

46:14.039 --> 46:16.474
A LOT OF PEOPLE MAKE MILLIONS
OF DOLLARS OFF OF ME.

46:16.507 --> 46:18.209
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT WOULD HAPPEN

46:18.243 --> 46:20.278
IF THIS WERE TO GET OUT?

46:20.311 --> 46:22.914
I'D LOSE MY FRIENDS,
MY TEAMMATES,

46:22.948 --> 46:26.184
MY FANS, MY ENDORSEMENTS.

46:28.519 --> 46:30.288
BUT MOST OF ALL,

46:30.321 --> 46:35.226
I'D LOSE THE THING THAT
I LOVE MOST IN THIS WORLD...

46:35.260 --> 46:38.196
PLAYING FOOTBALL.

46:40.331 --> 46:43.301
BESIDES, I LOVE SIERRA.

46:43.334 --> 46:47.305
I WANT A WIFE AND KIDS,
JUST LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE.

46:47.338 --> 46:48.506
- AND WHAT ABOUT US?

46:48.539 --> 46:51.109
- NOTHING HAS TO CHANGE.

46:51.142 --> 46:52.477
AND NOBODY NEEDS TO KNOW.

46:52.510 --> 46:56.982
IT'S NONE
OF THEIR GODDAMN BUSINESS.

47:01.552 --> 47:06.491
- YOU KNOW, EVERYTHING YOU SAID
MADE PERFECTLY GOOD SENSE...

47:06.524 --> 47:09.460
AND I'M SURE MOST PEOPLE
WOULD AGREE WITH YOU.

47:09.494 --> 47:14.199
WHY TELL ANYONE,
WHY LOSE EVERYTHING,

47:14.232 --> 47:18.503
WHEN IT CAN BE
YOUR LITTLE SECRET?

47:18.536 --> 47:23.341
BUT YOU SEE, IT WAS,
UH, DIFFERENT FOR ME.

47:23.374 --> 47:26.377
EVERYONE COULD TELL
WHO I WAS FROM THE START,

47:26.411 --> 47:29.347
WHICH, BELIEVE ME,
DIDN'T MAKE MY LIFE ANY EASIER.

47:29.380 --> 47:32.383
I'VE BEEN BEATEN UP,
CURSED AT,

47:32.417 --> 47:36.021
SPIT ON FROM DAY ONE,

47:36.054 --> 47:39.991
WHICH IN A WAY,
WAS WORTH IT...

47:41.426 --> 47:45.330
BECAUSE I'VE NEVER
HAD TO LIVE A LIE.

47:46.664 --> 47:51.569
AND I'M NOT ABOUT
TO START NOW,

47:51.602 --> 47:54.505
NOT FOR YOU,

47:54.539 --> 47:57.442
NOT FOR ANYONE.

48:03.214 --> 48:05.083
